sa:
   The Resource Monitor can also be opened on the → Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/Taskmgr_exe#win-taskmgr-tab-performance[Performance tab] of the [Task Manager (`Taskmgr.exe`)].

   → Windows/dirs/Windows/System32/perfmon_exe[`perfmon.exe`], the performance monitor
